&nbsp;
"You are contributing to the credibility of Italy at an international level at a complex moment - so always on X minister Crosetto turned to the Italian soldiers of the mission Kfor - Auguri to you, you serve the country away from home, and to your loved ones to whom my thanks goes. The Italians are proud of you!"
&nbsp;
"The Balkan stability is Italy's priority. With Mr Ejup Maqedonci - the Minister added - examined opportunities for cooperation with Kosovo Security Forces, to support the security and stability of the region. Finding together the way to make cooperation more and more effective." &nbsp;
&nbsp;
&nbsp;
<div </div
&nbsp;
"Excellent situation with General Ozkan Ulutas, NATO Commander KFOR. Italy ready to take up the Mission Command again, a fundamental commitment to the stability of the region and the whole of Europe" concluded.&nbsp;

